        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Recycling Infrastructure and Accessibility Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) to establish a pilot grant program for improving recycling accessibility in communities. The EPA may award grants to states, local governments, Indian tribes, or public-private partnerships.</p>]]>
        </text>
